Home Assistant FMD Integration
Copyright (c) 2025 Devin Slick

This integration is built to work with the FMD (Find My Device) project.

================================================================================

FMD (Find My Device) Project
https://fmd-foss.org

The FMD project provides the server and Android app that this integration
communicates with. FMD was created by Nulide and is maintained by Thore
and the FMD-FOSS team.

FMD Android App
https://gitlab.com/fmd-foss/fmd-android
License: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)

FMD Server
https://gitlab.com/fmd-foss/fmd-server
License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0)

FMD Project Maintainers:
- Nulide (Founder) - http://nulide.de
- Thore (Maintainer) - https://thore.io

This integration is a separate client that communicates with FMD servers
over the network. It does not incorporate or redistribute any FMD code.
This integration is licensed under the MIT License (see LICENSE file).

We are deeply grateful to the FMD team for creating this excellent
open source, privacy-respecting device tracking solution.

