================================================================================

Encryption Protocol Attribution:

This integration implements the FMD encryption protocol:
- RSA-3072 key exchange (designed by FMD team)
- AES-GCM data encryption (designed by FMD team)
- Argon2id password hashing (designed by FMD team)
- Command signing format (designed by FMD team)

The protocol design and implementation details are derived from analyzing
the FMD server source code and web client, which are open source under
AGPL-3.0 license.

